---

import Header from '../../components/Header'
import Footer from '../../components/Footer'
import RequestQuoteForm from '../../components/RequestQuoteForm'
import whitePhone from '../../assets/white-phone.svg'
import yardSign from '../../assets/yard-sign-Opt.jpg'
import love from '../../assets/love.svg'

---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" href="../../AlderFavicon.png" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
        <meta name="description" content="Alder Home Security ensures that you can find the best Memphis home security for your family. Here’s everything you should know about Memphis home security. " />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Memphis Home Security | Alder Home Security</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-white w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center">

        <Header path='/states/tennessee' client:load />

        <br/>

        <div class="w-full h-[325px] bg-cover bg-center max-w-6xl" style={{
            backgroundImage: 'url("https://res.cloudinary.com/alder/image/upload/q_auto,f_auto/v1566942110/Tennessee.jpg")'
        }}>
        <div class="w-full h-full flex flex-col items-center gap-8 justify-center bg-neutral-800/[.50]">

            <h1 class="text-white font-medium w-5/6 md:w-2/3 text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl text-center">Home Security Systems Memphis</h1>

            <a href="tel:800-710-1289" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:scale-105 transition duration-100 py-2 px-4 rounded-3xl border-2 z-10 border-white">
                <img alt="phone icon" src={whitePhone}/>
                <p class="text-white text-[15px]">Call Now 800-710-1289</p>
            </a>
            
        </div>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full max-w-6xl py-20 px-4 bg-white flex justify-center items-center ">

            <p class="text-[#58585B] leading-7 w-full md:w-4/5 lg:w-2/3 text-center">Those who live in Memphis know how many different home security systems there are in the city. Everyone seems to be using something new, and neighbors all use different security systems. Finding the right home security systems to use in your home in Memphis, TN can be difficult and frustrating. However, in the long run, finding the best monitoring security systems will be well worth your time. Here’s what Alder Home Security Systems has to say about finding the best Memphis home security systems.</p>

        </div>

        <RequestQuoteForm client:load bg_color="bg-[#61798F]" />

        <br/>
        <br/>

        <div class="w-full max-w-6xl bg-cover" style={{
            backgroundImage: 'url("https://res.cloudinary.com/alder/image/upload/q_auto,f_auto/v1557271904/Map_Screen_Shot.png")'
        }} >
        <div class="w-full h-full bg-[#297CA3]/[.50] flex flex-col items-center py-4 px-6 gap-4 justify-evenly">
                <h2 class="flex flex-row items-center text-2xl sm:text-6xl text-white font-medium gap-2 bg-neutral-800/[.75] p-2 rounded-xl ">WE <img alt="heart" class=" w-[30px] h-[30px] sm:w-[65px] sm:h-[65px]" src={love}/> MEMPHIS </h2>

                <p class="text-white bg-neutral-800/[.85] text-sm md:text-base w-full md:w-2/3 p-4 leading-6 ">Here at Alder Home Security, we ensure to make security systems and monitoring systems that will keep your family safe in Memphis, TN. Our Memphis office is aware of all dangers, concerns, and problems that you may be worried about. This is because Alder Home Security loves Memphis and our customers in Memphis. We treat our customers as if they are family and we make sure that they are 100% taken care of. If you ever have any concerns or issues, will be there at your side to take care of you. When you join our team, you can call us your family.</p>
        </div>
        </div>

        <br/>
        <br/>

        <div class="w-full max-w-4xl bg-cover bg-center " style={{
            backgroundImage: `url(${yardSign})`
        }} >
        <div class="w-full h-full bg-neutral-800/[.75] md:bg-neutral-800/[.45] flex flex-col justify-center gap-4 py-8 px-4 md:px-12">

            <h3 class="text-white text-2xl">Your Neighbor's</h3>

            <h3 class="text-white text-4xl font-medium">Opinion Matters</h3>

            <p class="text-white text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium md:w-1/2 leading-6">Even if your neighbors all have different systems, their opinions matter. You might not want to put too much stock in their opinions of the companies that they use. Instead, pay attention to the type of system that they have. Ask if they like a DIY system or a traditional system. See what they like and dislike about their types of systems. Even ask them to show you how the system works and see what you like and dislike about the differences in the systems. They will be able to help you decide what system you want to get in Memphis, TN. This helps because your neighbors are familiar with the situations that you come across in Memphis and so they know what you need and what you don’t need. This will help you know what will work best in your neighborhood.</p>

        </div>
        </div>

        <br/>
        <br/>

        <div class="w-full max-w-6xl flex flex-col items-center">
            <div class="w-full h-[250px] bg-cover" style={{
                backgroundImage: 'url("https://res.cloudinary.com/alder/image/upload/v1557333574/simple.jpg")',
                backgroundPosition: "center 85%"
            }} />

            <div class="w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-between gap-4 md:gap-0 md:flex-row px-4 py-12 ">

                <div class=" w-full md:w-[25%] flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-4">
                    <h3 class="text-[#58585B] font-medium text-2xl text-center md:text-left ">Differences in Alarm Systems</h3>
                </div>

                <p class="text-[#58585B] text-sm leading-6 w-full md:w-[65%] " >
                    There are a few different security systems that you can choose from. The first alarm system that you can choose is a traditional monitor. This means that a security company will come to your home and set up the system. These types of systems are efficient and easy. However, they are a more expensive option. So, for those working with a budget, this might not be the best monitoring alarm system for you to choose. For those working with a budget, the best system is a DIY. They are cheaper and give you the same control as a traditional system. You can set up the system on your own and place it wherever you want.
                </p>

            </div>

        </div>
        
    
        <Footer />

    </body>
</html>